    "Management": {
      "text": "Low-dose\nCorticosteroids\ntypically produce rapid response\n[4]\nExample regimen:\nPrednisone\n15 mg PO QD for 2-4 weeks\nNeeds to start a year-long taper after the first month, so write enough for them to get in with PCP.\nAvoid\nNSAIDs\nif history of or concern for\nGCA\ndue to risk of renal injury",
